title: The Important iPhone 15 Pro Feature Nobody's Talking About!
description:
3nm SoC, USB-C a new 120mm camera, a new Watch feature that *isn't*, and a lot more nobody has talked about!
Looking for a powerful new browser? Try @SigmaOS for free! https://go.sigmaos.com/snazzylabs

Apple's September iPhone 15 event paled in comparison to WWDC, but that doesn't mean things were bad! A whole slew of new updates from last year made it to the standard iPhone 15, all iPhone models gained USB-C (FINALLY!) the new iPhone 15 Pro found titanium, and the 15 Pro Max acquired a prismatic zoom lens. Apple Watch got some updates, a new UWB chip made it into all new devices, and software features involving satellite roadside assistance and portrait mode are sure to make a splash. But we should probably talk about something Apple kinda just blew past. AAA gaming on the iPhone with Assassin's Creed Mirage, Resident Evil, and Death Stranding...
